    <h1>How it affects Women everyday!</h1>
    <h4>By being told from a young age about female "ideals", women grow up to feel hesitant around their male counterparts because of their ideals to be quiet and also because of the oppresion they face due to either being the minority in their workplace, or due to sexist comments. Women with full-time jobs still earn 77% of their male counterparts' earnings. This oppression then creates sexism in the workplace and in society.</h4>
        
